lands Bulldogs football|Redlands Bulldogs]]'''\n| 9\n| 1990\n| 2019\n| 0\n| 9\n| 9\n| {{Winning percentage|0|9}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[RPI Engineers football|Rensselaer Engineers]]\n| 6\n| 1999\n| 2018\n| 5\n| 6\n| 11\n| {{Winning percentage|5|6}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Rhodes Lynx football|Rhodes Lynx]]\n| 1\n| 1988\n| 1988\n| 0\n| 1\n| 1\n| {{Winning percentage|0|1}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Rochester Yellowjackets football|Rochester Yellowjackets]]\n| 1\n| 1987\n| 1987\n| 0\n| 1\n| 1\n| {{Winning percentage|0|1}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Rose-Hulman Fightin' Engineers football|Rose\u2013Hulman Fightin' Engineers]]\n| 1\n| 2016\n| 2016\n| 0\n| 1\n| 1\n| {{Winning percentage|0|1}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Rowan Profs football|Rowan Profs]]\n| 16\n| 1991\n| 2014\n| 31\n| 16\n| 47\n| {{Winning percentage|31|16}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[St. John Fisher Cardinals football|St. John Fisher Cardinals]]\n| 5\n| 2004\n| 2013\n| 10\n| 5\n| 15\n| {{Winning percentage|10|5}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| '''[[Saint John's Johnnies football|Saint John's (MN) Johnnies]]'''\n| 26\n| 1976\n| 2019\n| 42\n| 24\n| 66\n| {{Winning percentage|42|24}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[St. Lawrence Saints football|St. Lawrence Saints]]\n| 4\n| 1976\n| 2010\n| 2\n| 4\n| 6\n| {{Winning percentage|2|4}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[St. Norbert Green Knights football|St. Norbert Green Knights]]\n| 13\n| 1989\n| 2018\n| 2\n| 13\n| 15\n| {{Winning percentage|2|13}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[St. Olaf Oles football|St. Olaf Oles]]\n| 1\n| 1978\n| 1978\n| 0\n| 1\n| 1\n| {{Winning percentage|0|1}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[St. Scholastica Saints football|St. Scholastica Saints]]\n| 5\n| 2011\n| 2015\n| 0\n| 5\n| 5\n| {{Winning percentage|0|5}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[St. Thomas Tommies football|St. Thomas (MN) Tommies]]\n| 9\n| 1990\n| 2017\n| 20\n| 9\n| 29\n| {{Winning percentage|2