ie]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" | {{ct|ALM|1998}}\n| style=\"background:#E4B3AB;\" | [[Bo Hamburger]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 4|4]]\n| [[Jeroen Blijlevens]]\n| style=\"background:#FFEB64;\" rowspan=\"3\" | [[Stuart O'Grady]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Stuart O'Grady]]\n| style=\"background:#E4B3AB;\" | [[Jacky Durand]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 5|5]]\n| [[Mario Cipollini]]\n| style=\"background:#9CE97B;\" rowspan=\"17\" | [[Erik Zabel]]\n| style=\"background:#E4B3AB;\" | [[Aart Vierhouten]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 6|6]]\n| [[Mario Cipollini]]\n| style=\"background:#E4B3AB;\" | [[Max Sciandri]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 7|7]]\n| [[Jan Ullrich]]\n| style=\"background:#FFEB64;\" | [[Jan Ullrich]]\n| style=\"background:#FFA8A4;\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Stefano Zanini]]\n| rowspan=\"15\"|[[Jan Ullrich]]\n| {{ct|THR|1998}}\n| ''no award''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 8|8]]\n| [[Jacky Durand]]\n| style=\"background:#FFEB64;\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Laurent Desbiens]]\n| rowspan=\"14\" | {{ct|COF|1998}}\n| style=\"background:#E4B3AB;\"|[[Andrea Tafi (cyclist)|Andrea Tafi]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 9|9]]\n| [[L\u00e9on van Bon]]\n| style=\"background:#FFA8A4;\" | [[Jens Voigt]]\n| style=\"background:#E4B3AB;\" | [[Jens Voigt]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 10|10]]\n| [[Rodolfo Massi]]\n| style=\"background:#FFEB64;\" rowspan=\"5\"|[[Jan Ullrich]]\n| style=\"background:#FFA8A4;\" rowspan=\"8\"|[[Rodolfo Massi]]\n| style=\"background:#E4B3AB;\"|[[C\u00e9dric Vasseur]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 11|11]]\n| [[Marco Pantani]]\n| style=\"background:#E4B3AB;\"|[[Roland Meier]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1998 Tour de France, Stage 12 to Stage 2